Manager: Alright, first let me give you a rough
explanation of the job.

Manager: As for the tasks, it would include
reception at the cash register, cleaning of
private rooms, organizing DVDs, and delivering
products to the private rooms.

(The job content is pretty much as I expected.
It's basic stuff, so I should get used to it
quickly.)

(If I also know the preferences of the customers,
it seems like things will go smoothly.)

Um, what kind of movies do the customers who come

Manager: Well, we have a lot of amateur pick-up,
schoolgirl, and aphrodisiac sex videos.

(C-Could it be... videos, as in... that kind of

(Rei-san's reaction... so that's what it
meant...!)
Manager (Hehe♡ His face is turning bright red...♡)

Manager (I thought it was strange for such a
beautiful person to come, but I guess they didn't
know what kind of store we are...♪)

Manager (This seems like it'll be fun...♡ Let's
throw a little jab...)

Manager: By the way, um, Ayako-san, are you
familiar with AV?

Huh!?... Eh!? W-Well... I'm not really... familiar

Manager: Well, you see, in our line of work, it's
important to have knowledge about those kinds of

Manager: Customers sometimes ask for

Manager: Well, since it's your first time, I'll

Manager: There's a manual under the register, so
make sure to study it before the customers arrive.

Manager: Well then, I'll leave the reception to

Store Manager: Yes, yes. For example, amateur

Store Manager: No matter how much you watch AV,
new releases come out at a pace that surpasses it,
so you can't watch them all...! It's like the
universe itself!!!

(The universe... might be an exaggeration, but
there are so many different videos being
released... It's a bit overwhelming... No, let's
just focus on the genres of our work for now...)

(Alright... for the first one... First Shoot JK -

(Next is... Thick Vibrator! \.\.in In the a**...

(As for the third one...! ...Wait, \CE[31]what is

(I guess... I have no choice but to ask...)
Um... excuse me... what genre is this DVD?

Manager: Ah... my eyesight is a bit bad, but could

Umm... umm... 'Nhooh! My pussy is tingling!! Semen

Manager: Ah, that's a sex video♡ Nice to meet you.

Manager: Ah...! Th-That DVD is... 'The Complete

I-I'm sorry... It wasn't intentional... B-But I

Manager: That's something that happens often!!
Which one do you think is more important, wiping

I'm sorry! I'll make sure to compensate for it...

Manager: It's fine... It wasn't intentional...
Besides, even if it's compensated for, this DVD is

(I-I feel a chill...! C-Could it be... if I feel

(T-This is bad...! All the faith I've gathered...!

(If there's something that can serve as a

(I guess there's no choice but to offer a

U-Um... Manager-san... I have a little proposal...

Manager: Oh my, I never expected Ayako-kun to be

Manager: Oh, could it be because of the influence

So, is that all you wanted to talk about? It's not

You're planning to spread the word about me

Manager: ...But, since you're in the position of
